 throughout</p></div></div><div data-w-id="0e331148-2df2-4cc1-ea98-909bd35be803" class="focused-icon-block focused-no-bottom-border"><div class="focused-icon-left margin-top-ten"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/66f1ffecdef9310969f57d0d_Clock%20Icon.svg" alt="Clock Icon" width="37" height="51" class="autofit"></div><div class="focused-text-right"><div class="heading-five text-white">3. Fitout Construction &amp; Handover</div><p class="margin-top-fifteen text-light-grey">We coordinate and complete your full commercial fitout — managing trades, installing fixtures, and finishing every detail to spec. From flooring to feature lighting, we ensure your space is delivered on time, defect-free, and ready for business.</p></div></div></div><div class="about-one-focused-right"><div style="opacity: 1;" class="about-one-focused-image-one"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/674f9b92faa922f1c9d341e8_ENP01158%20(Large).jpg" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 645px" width="645" height="481" alt="ENP Fitouts project team on site at commercial fitout" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/674f9b92faa922f1c9d341e8_ENP01158%20(Large)-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/674f9b92faa922f1c9d341e8_ENP01158%20(Large)-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/674f9b92faa922f1c9d341e8_ENP01158%20(Large)-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/674f9b92faa922f1c9d341e8_ENP01158%20(Large)-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/674f9b92faa922f1c9d341e8_ENP01158%20(Large).jpg 1620w" class="autofit responsive-full-width"></div><div style="opacity: 0;" class="about-one-focused-image-two"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66f1ffebdef9310969f57940/674f9b802ae4a2d428b5a641_ENP05602-2%20(Large).jpg" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 645px" width=